classAssociation.name: at
classAssociation.description: A Product is at a Machine (either machine or divice)

useCase.name: Aggregate (give) attributes to Products
useCase.description:
This use case provides an understanding about how machines collaboratively aggregate attributes to products.
1- Product is passed from input devices to output devices, both of which have infinite capacity.
2 - When product exists inside of a machine, that machine may give some attribute to the product.
3 - Only one product may exist at a given time in most machines (with the only exception being that more than one may exist in input and output devices).

action.precondition: m1.connected = m2 and m2.sort = ismachine and m2.ready = true
